  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ここにいる貴族の跡取りは
かなり食べ物の好き嫌いが激しいらしい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The heir to the noble family here is apparently
pretty intense about what he likes and doesn't like.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>彼がなにかを残す度に
食材が無駄にされていくんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's wasting food every time he acts like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Unsure about this exact phrasing.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんな事は許せない。
俺は、食材を守り抜いてみせる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't let him do that.
I have to protect the ingredients!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そこまで頑張って
守り抜くものなのかしら……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is it necessary to go all out to protect that...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
